  "body": "### Component\n\nAnvil\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [ ] Foundry\n- [ ] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\n_No response_\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\nanvil 0.1.0 (226affb 2022-09-27T00:13:00.191026Z)\n\n### Operating System\n\nmacOS (Apple Silicon)\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nwith `mumbai = ...` in `[rpc_endpoints]` in `foundry.toml`,\r\n\r\n```\r\nanvil --rpc-url mumbai\r\nthread 'main' panicked at 'Failed to establish provider to fork url: Invalid provider url: mumbai\r\n\r\nCaused by:\r\n   0: builder error: relative URL without a base\r\n   1: relative URL without a base\r\n```",
